---
import founderImage from "../assets/founder-1.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAF7F2] py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-14 px-5 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:gap-16">
    <div>
      <img
        src={founderImage.src}
        alt="Aravind Kumar"
        class="h-[520px] w-full rounded-[2rem] object-cover sm:h-[680px] lg:rounded-[3rem]"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#D97706] sm:text-sm">
        From The Founder
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1F2937] sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
        Our work begins by seeing the child before the challenge.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-[#1F2937]/72 md:text-xl md:leading-9">
        <p>
          Children First was born from a simple belief: potential is everywhere, but opportunity is not. When a child receives steady encouragement, patient teaching and a community that knows their name, something powerful begins to shift.
        </p>

        <p>
          We are here to make that support feel close, consistent and human. Every program, partnership and conversation is shaped around the dignity of the child and the future they are brave enough to imagine.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 border-t border-[#1F2937]/15 pt-8">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1F2937]">
          Aravind Kumar
        </p>

        <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-[#1F2937]/65">
          Founder
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
